{"url": "https://life.laseraway.com/smile/8-outfit-planning-apps-to-simplify-your-life", "text": "1. ClosetSpace\n\nClosetSpace is a mobile app that enables you to catalog all your clothes to create an electronic wardrobe. How does it work? Simple. You upload images of your clothes using your smartphone camera. You can then group items based on color, garment type, and number of times worn. From that, you can also create lists and outfits, coding outfits according to events, such as dates, work, etc. The cool thing about ClosetSpace is that you can actually view statistics on how often you wear clothing items, so you can decide what to toss and what to keep.", "images": ["https://life.laseraway.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Imported_Blog_Media/pinterest_cjnq3j_xdvdvx.png?width=31&name=pinterest_cjnq3j_xdvdvx.png", "https://life.laseraway.com/hs-fs/hubfs/LaserAway_April2018/Img/facebook%20(1).png?width=25&height=25&name=facebook%20(1).png", "https://life.laseraway.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Smile%20Blog%20Photos/Stylicious-e1522801287855_q5fllc-249x300.png?width=249&height=300&name=Stylicious-e1522801287855_q5fllc-249x300.png", "https://life.laseraway.com/hs/cta/cta/default/2353558/39997a43-29b4-4d5e-ab0d-26b8906a7645.png", "https://life.laseraway.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Imported_Blog_Media/instagram_jmytaq_dwr3kh.png?width=31&name=instagram_jmytaq_dwr3kh.png", "https://life.laseraway.com/hs-fs/hubfs/LaserAway_April2018/Img/youtube-1.png?width=31&name=youtube-1.png", "https://life.laseraway.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Smile%20Blog%20Photos/Pureple-Outfit-Planner-e1522801324563_v5mxjg-249x300.png?width=249&height=300&name=Pureple-Outfit-Planner-e1522801324563_v5mxjg-249x300.png", "https://life.laseraway.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Smile%20Blog%20Photos/Closfy-e1522801228889_ljy0px-249x300.png?width=249&height=300&name=Closfy-e1522801228889_ljy0px-249x300.png", "https://life.laseraway.com/hs/cta/cta/default/2353558/33849cf1-5d12-4ba3-a7b6-82f25b7f03d9.png", "https://life.laseraway.com/hs-fs/hubfs/LaserAway_April2018/Img/twit